{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji14","name":"毛泽东全集第14卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji14.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给吕超\"的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给吕超\"的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1939年10月7日）汉群先生左右："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王右瑜先生到延安，接谈甚快。奉读大示，向往尤深。先生翊赞中枢，功高望重，下风引领，敢不拜嘉。国难当前，团结为第一义，此物此志，当与先生同之也。敬复。即颂勋祉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弟毛泽东上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月七日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]吕超（1890一1951），字汉群，四川宜宾人。当时任国民党政府参军长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快无"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比t生毛泽东致吕超信的手稿。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1939,"month":10,"day":7}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":125,"page_end":126},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}